<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Hey all I'm working on a guide for enchanters.  I am focusing on soloing because thats how I really got a grasp of how my spells worked, but I am also doing quests, group spots, group roles, items, stats, etc.. I was curious if anyone has any feedback/info they could share with me.  I am looking specificly for soloing from 18 - 24 because I cant remember where I did that anymore =). So if you have anything that could be helpful, or want a copy when I'm done/rough drafts.  Email me at justinkonecny@hotmail.com since I proly won't check this again 8Þ. </p>
