<p>Level 9-11 Field of Bones on the Wall using Pet  <br />Level 10 - 15 Kurn <br />Level 15-18 Misty Thicket (slow xp but good plat and raises faction in Riverdale) <br />Level 18-21 Oasis <br />Level 21-24 Kerra (This is a great place to get good at charm and I never saw anyone else.  At 24 most is blue or light blue, but lots of MOBS) <br /> <br />Addition from  <br /> <br />25-28 Nederia's Landing is great. Start on the waterfall side with lower MOBS then move to the water to fight frogs.  With enduring breath you level and up swimming.  Then go to far side to hunt bears.  Plat is not good, but no one hunts here so plenty to lvl quick. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Thu Jan 26 13:51:35 2006 by hcs</span></i></p>
